          <title>Lawyer in Diego Pavia's eligibility lawsuit against NCAA cites NBA draft pick's return to college</title>
          <description><![CDATA[A lawyer for Heisman Trophy runner-up Diego Pavia and 26 other football players has cited the NCAA’s decision to allow an NBA draft pick to return to college basketball as a reason that a federal judge should let his clients play in 2026 and 2027.]]></description>
